                     <interp inst="t17981205-24-person413" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            's house.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you remember one of the witnesses coming to you with that check - have you seen that check before? - A. I am not certain that I have.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you recollect any person coming with a check? - A. I cannot say I did.</p>
               <p>Q. Then do you know the hand-writing of 
               <persName id="t17981205-24-person414">
                  William
                   Golding
               <interp inst="t17981205-24-person414" type="surname" value="Golding"></interp>
