                     <interp inst="t17981205-24-person415" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             that keeps cash at your house? - A. No.</p>
               <p>Q. Where is the shop that you keep? - A. No. 21, Lombard-street.</p>
               <p>Q. I see that is dated No. 2I, Lombard-street? - A. It is one of our shop checks.</p>
               <p>Q. There is no person of that name in your house? - A. None.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know any person of that name, 
               <persName id="t17981205-24-person416">
                  William
                   Golding
               <interp inst="t17981205-24-person416" type="surname" value="Golding"></interp>
