             sworn. - I searched the prisoner in our office, and found upon him these checks,(producing them); four filled up, and six blank.</p>
               <p>Q. Look at that check, (the check in question); do they appear to be in the same hand-writing? - 
               <persName id="t17981205-24-person424">
                  A. 
               <interp inst="t17981205-24-person424" type="given" value="A."></interp>
